        <div class="section">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Lox Player is a powerful, privacy-focused media player designed to give you complete control over your
                video and audio experience. Built with modern technology and user privacy in mind, Lox Player offers a
                seamless way to enjoy your media collection.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>We believe in creating software that respects your privacy while delivering an exceptional user
                experience. Lox Player is built on the principle that your media should remain yours - no tracking, no
                data collection, just pure functionality.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <p>Lox Player is designed to be your all-in-one media solution:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Video Player:</strong> Play all video formats with advanced controls</li>
                <li><strong>Music Player:</strong> Beautiful audio player with playlist support</li>
                <li><strong>File Manager:</strong> Browse and organize your media files</li>
                <li><strong>Online Streaming:</strong> Stream content from URLs</li>
                <li><strong>Privacy First:</strong> No data collection, everything stays local</li>
                <li><strong>Fast & Smooth:</strong> Optimized performance for all devices</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Technology</h2>
            <p>Lox Player is built using:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Flutter:</strong> Cross-platform framework for beautiful, native apps</li>
                <li><strong>Riverpod:</strong> State management for reactive UI</li>
                <li><strong>Video Player:</strong> High-performance video playback</li>
                <li><strong>Just Audio:</strong> Professional audio player engine</li>
                <li><strong>Modern Architecture:</strong> Clean code principles and best practices</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

